              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
                <td class="p-3 font-semibold">Non-Ferrous (Brass) Clutch</td>
                <td class="p-3 text-yellow-600">Low</td>
                <td class="p-3">Acceptable for many C1D2 applications</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="p-3 font-semibold">Direct Drive Coupling + VFD</td>
